Value: Lithium Energy Limited, a battery minerals company, engages in the exploration and development of lithium and graphite mineral properties. The company develops its flagship property Solaroz Lithium Brine Project comprising approximately 12,000 hectares of lithium mineral tenements located in Argentina. It also holds 100% interest in Burke Graphite Project located in the Cloncurry region in North Central Queensland. Lithium Energy Limited was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
